dct_title_s: Subdivision plat of East Rutherford Industrial Park section a for Bergen County Associates, et als, Borough of East Rutherford, Bergen County, N.J.
dct_description_sm: This map shows the riparian line along Berry's Creek for subdivision East Rutherford Industrial Park, Section A.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Being a subdivision of lots 5F, 7D, 8A, 8B, and part of lots 9, 10 & 11 Block 106 Sheet 11 East Rutherford tax assessment map.
